Invocation Name: indian football quiz
des: Play an interesting quiz on the Indian Super League with Alexa. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. This quiz sets up 10 questions to test your trivia with India's very own premier league.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
